title: Carrie Fisher and Serena Shahidi are Wishfully Drinking
description: Hold on to your space buns, this week we're talking about a book that's legit good!!! Serena Shahidi (@glamdemon2004) joins Claire (@clairethescare) and Ashley (@ashleyhammm) to talk about the incredible Carrie Fisher. You'll laugh, you'll cry, it's a really good one I swear.
